## рЯЦ•пЄП Output Compatibility

| Software | Format | Status |
|---|---|---|
| Blender 3.x / 4.x | `.obj` | вЬЕ Imports with correct geometry, normals, UV |
| Unity 2022 LTS | `.obj` | вЬЕ Asset import with default settings |
| Unreal Engine 5 | `.obj` | вЬЕ Import via Content Browser |
| MeshLab | `.obj` | вЬЕ Renders correctly |
| Windows 3D Viewer | `.obj` | вЬЕ Opens directly |
| Photoshop / Substance | `.png` normal map | вЬЕ Blue-channel normal map standard |
| Three.js | `.obj` via OBJLoader | вЬЕ Correct vertex and UV data |

