## рЯУИ Performance Reference

| Grid Size | Vertices | Triangles | Approx. Time |
|---|---|---|---|
| 64 √Ч 64 | 4,096 | 7,938 | < 0.3s |
| 128 √Ч 128 | 16,384 | 32,258 | < 1.2s |
| 256 √Ч 256 | 65,536 | 130,050 | ~3s |
| 512 √Ч 512 | 262,144 | 523,778 | ~10s |

*Tested on Intel Core i7-1165G7, 16 GB RAM.*

---

## рЯФЃ Possible Extensions

- **Multi-scale terrain** вАФ blend height maps at multiple frequencies for fractal detail
- **ML depth estimation** вАФ replace luminance proxy with a MiDaS/DPT depth network
- **Mesh decimation** вАФ reduce polygon count in flat areas while preserving ridges
- **glTF 2.0 export** вАФ embed PBR materials (normal, roughness, metallic maps)
- **Spherical projection** вАФ map onto a UV sphere for planetary terrain
- **Web app** вАФ FastAPI backend + Three.js frontend for browser-based generation

